{"id":29527229929,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG3_XF6Q","head_branch":"DHIS2-21842-userstore-flushmode","head_sha":"ab36823cddecbb9ee3280b12fb663d40c4bba4eb","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":51167,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: skip auto-flush on getUserByUsername read-only lookup (DHIS2-21842)","status":"completed","conclusion":"failure","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":79953818296,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASnZ5yuA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29527229929","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29527229929","created_at":"2026-07-16T19:14:44Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T19:28:02Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-16T19:14:44Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29527229929/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29527229929/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/79953818296","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29527229929/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29527229929/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29527229929/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix: skip auto-flush on getUserByUsername read-only lookup (DHIS2-21842)\n\nUnder the default FlushModeType.AUTO, the JPQL username lookup forces a full\npersistence-context auto-flush before every execution. In bulk metadata-import\npaths (e.g. updating a UserRole with tens of thousands of members) this method\nis called once per user while the session keeps growing, so each auto-flush\ndirty-checks an ever-larger context -\u003e O(n^2) CPU (observed: ~90 min pinned to a\ncore for 22k members).\n\nSetting FlushModeType.COMMIT makes the read-only lookup skip the pre-query flush,\ncollapsing O(n^2) -\u003e O(n); the session is still flushed at the import's existing\nstage-boundary flush. Behaviorally inert for clean sessions (login, current-user\nlookups); a username lookup not seeing same-transaction unflushed rows is already\nguarded by the DB username unique constraint.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Claude","email":"noreply@anthropic.com"},"id":"ab36823cddecbb9ee3280b12fb663d40c4bba4eb","tree_id":"8e07e82fd8f5d5d2e1a02c7882ddeff130191ea1","timestamp":"2026-07-16T17:41:44Z","committer":{"name":"Claude","email":"noreply@anthropic.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core","fork":false,"private":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core","archive_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/{archive_format}{/ref}","assignee